title: Plant Based News LIES (Retraction & Apology?)
description: PlantBasedNews must (repeat: must) issue a retraction and an apology for the false claims you made about me (and my "financial misconduct") and they should be willing to report THE REAL FACTS of the case instead.  I told the truth about this case AT EVERY STAGE, and many other vegans lined up for their opportunity to defame me.  Klaus, IF YOUR CHANNEL is regarded as more trustworthy (as "news") than Durianrider, you must realize that a lie of this kind (told to 29,000 people) does serious harm to my reputation: you know this is false, and you have been totally irresponsible in how you handled this affair.  PlantBasedNews may be a scam, but à-bas-le-ciel is not.
